@startuml sequence-progression
title Level Progression — Sequential Lock + Page Gating + ★3 Hint Carryover
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
actor User
participant "TitleScene" as Title
participant "GameScene" as GS
participant "ResultScene" as RS
participant "SaveManager" as SM
participant "IndexedDB\n(progress + meta)" as IDB

== Title 진입 — 페이지 + 잠금 상태 표시 ==
User -> Title : enter
Title -> SM : list() (progress 전체)
SM -> IDB : transaction(readonly)
IDB --> SM : [{ mapId, stars }, ...]
SM --> Title : records
Title -> Title : page = 1 (1-100 표시)
note right of Title
  페이지 잠금:
    page 2 → bestStars[100] ≥ 1
    page 3 → bestStars[200] ≥ 1
  맵 잠금:
    mapId N → bestStars[N-1] ≥ 1
    (1번은 항상 해제)
end note

== 화살표로 페이지 이동 ==
User -> Title : tap right arrow
alt 잠금 해제됨
  Title -> Title : page++ , scrollY = 0
else 잠금
  note right of Title : 무시 (사운드 없음)
end

== 맵 카드 탭 ==
User -> Title : tap map N
alt isMapUnlocked(N)
  Title -> GS : transition("game", { map })
else 잠김
  note right of Title : 자물쇠 표시, 무시
end

== GameScene 진입 (신규) — hint 보충 적용 ==
GS -> SM : consumeHintCarryover()
SM -> IDB : meta["hint_carryover"] → 0 으로 리셋
SM --> GS : extraHints (예: 1)
GS -> GS : hints = map.hintCount + extraHints
note right of GS
  mapId % 8 === 0 이면
  hints = max(hints, 3) "8마다 채우기"
end note
GS -> GS : new Hint(board, hints)

== 게임 종료 → ResultScene ==
GS -> RS : transition("result", { score, stars, mapId, ... })
alt cleared (stars ≥ 1)
  RS -> SM : saveBest(record)
  SM -> IDB : progress.put(mapId, ...)
  alt stars === 3
    RS -> SM : addHintCarryover()
    SM -> IDB : meta["hint_carryover"] += 1
    note right of RS : 다음 진입 시 자동 +1
  end
end

== 다음 → / 다시하기 ==
User -> RS : tap "다음"
alt hasNext (cleared && N < maxMapId)
  RS -> GS : transition("game", { map: N+1 })
  GS -> SM : consumeHintCarryover() (위 흐름 반복)
else 비활성
  note right of RS : 실패/마지막 맵 → 무시
end

User -> RS : tap "🏠 타이틀"
RS -> Title : transition("title")
Title -> SM : list() (재로드 — 새 별/잠금 반영)
@enduml
